snippet.title: Mecha BREAK | Closed Beta Trailer
snippet.description:
Emerged as a pivotal substance shaping global trends, EIC is the magic behind humanity's industrial marvels, and the spark for relentless conflicts.

Now, more never-before-seen BREAK Strikers from rival factions are entering the battle. Another upheaval is on the horizon...

Gear up for Mecha BREAK's Closed Beta. Registration opens soon! Sign-up here: https://seasun.ink/3PsnSMi

For more information, please visit the official website: https://www.mechabreak.comRecruitment 
Steam store page: https://www.seasun.ink/Mecha_BREAK_EN

Join Mecha BREAK on social media:
Discord: https://www.discord.gg/4a6d7Ga8RB
X (Twitter): https://www.twitter.com/MechaBREAK

#mechabreak
